content: I played this game when i was a little girl. Im so excited to be able to share it with my daughter! Thank you so much for making this mobile! I forgot about putt putt ‚ù§ he was always my favorite!!!!!!! I changed my review becuase the game no longer works for me. :(
Even better than I remember it! A nice trip down memory lane

These are great old games. Too bad the audio quality can't be updated. It can be a bit grating. Also 1 star cause this app randomly downloads updates every few months or so. It's a bit suspicious. Maybe some bug?

Terrific game in the series.  Easy controls teach comprehensive problem solving for young minds. Cute, colorful, musical; everything kids enjoy.

Not too happy with the mobile game. The dialog and music seems sped up. Definitely not the same music tone as my desktop games. Other than that it's still the good old gameplay I remember playing as a kid

I grew up on Humongous Entertainment games!! I love Putt Putt. Great childhood flashback haha. I just wish they had an option to skip through all the talking like the original game used to. Takes forever when you have to listen to everyone and you can't get the game played as quickly as the original. This would be a fantastic feature to add!
Won't let me refund!

So I have been trying for two hours to get it to load. Keeps saying checking license. My son is impatient. He loves putt putt as much as I did when I was kid. I don't want to refund and have it charge my card again just to get it to work. And it's on wifi. Only thing on wifi so it shouldn't take 2 hours to load. Other putt putt games didn't take this long to load. Very not pleased.
This games is great and I have no issues for me.
Unfortunately, none of these wonderful games will open on my galaxy 5. So disappointing! I hope they fix the problem.

I don't care if I'm 18 I grew up with putt-putt. Glad he's on my mobile device

I HAD to buy both putt putt games I saw! Not just cause I knew my 5 year old daughter would love it, but because I want to play it, too! And im 26 haha! This was the very first computer game I ever played in Kindergarten. Brings back so many good memories!! (:
